patch.comment: dev-server: add ipv6 loopback address support in terminal output
add debug log when Webpack is imported from the rig package

minor.comment: Allow infrastructure logs to be printed.
Use project-level webpack dependency when it's installed.
Normalize import of builtin modules to use the `node:` protocol.

Update the `webpack` peer dependency to `^5.82.1` from `~5.82.1`. Also bump `webpack-dev-server` to `^5.1.0`. This drops support for Node 16 and includes some breaking configuration changes. See https://github.com/webpack/webpack-dev-server/blob/master/migration-v5.md.

patch.comment: Include CHANGELOG.md in published releases again

minor.comment: Add `onGetWatchOptions` accessor hook to allow cooperating plugins to, for example, configure a list of globs for the file watcher to ignore.

patch.comment: Fix line endings in published package.
Update type-only imports to include the type modifier.

minor.comment: Move loading of webpack config file into the `onLoadConfiguration` hook to allow other plugins to define fallback behavior, rather than only overriding the config file.

patch.comment: Bump webpack to v5.82.1
Improve the error message when the "--serve" is incorrectly specified
Update webpack to v5.80.0
Fix bug where peerDep of webpack was not properly updated with regular dependency version.
Bump webpack to 5.78.0

minor.comment: Add support for `.cjs` and `.mjs` file extensions for webpack config files, in addition to the `.js` file extension.

patch.comment: Upgrade to webpack 5.75.0
Log errors and warnings from nested compilations.
Set WebSocket port to match http port.
Upgrade webpack-dev-server
fix: removed deprecation warning for webpack-dev-server
Fix an issue where Heft will crash if the Webpack configuration is an empty array.
Rename the "master" branch to "main".

minor.comment: Change "webpack" to be a peer dependency instead of a regular dependency; this avoids a situation where Heft might import a different version of Webpack from the consuming project or its rig

patch.comment: Update the package.json repository field to include the directory property.
Upgrade the `@types/node` dependency to version to version 12.
Upgrades webpack 5 to get a bug fix when resolving modules with a # in the path
Fix webpack5 persistent cache in production mode
